spec_data.Name: perl-Apache-LogRegex
spec_data.Description:
Designed as a simple class to parse Apache log files.  It will construct
a regex that will parse the given log file format and can then parse
lines from the log file line by line returning a hash of each line.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:03:33 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parse a line from an Apache logfile into a hash
